<aside id="contribute" class="contribute">
  <h3>Add your app to the gallery</h3>
  <ol>
    <li>Drop your screenshot(s) in <code>src/assets/gallery/&lt;slug&gt;/</code>.</li>
    <li>Copy <code>src/content/apps/rocco.md</code> to <code>src/content/apps/&lt;slug&gt;.md</code> and edit the frontmatter. Schema is enforced at build time — bad PRs won't merge.</li>
    <li>Open a PR. Card lands in the grid on merge.</li>
  </ol>
</aside>
